<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>How It Works | MindMate</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #7e57c2;
      --primary-dark: #5e35b1;
      --accent: #4dd0e1;
      --text-light: #fefefe;
      --text-muted: #b0b8c1;
      --bg-dark: #0f1117;
      --card-dark: #1a1d24;
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: var(--bg-dark);
      --text: var(--text-light);
      --card-bg: var(--card-dark);
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    header, section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    p {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 1rem auto;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .steps {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature {
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .step {
      background-color: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .step:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .step h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .step p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.7rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  

  <header>
    <%- include('../partials/nav', { user: user }) %>
</header>
    <h1>How MindMate Works</h1>
    <p>MindMate helps you solve problems, debug code, build products, and make smart decisions ‚Äî all powered by AI.</p>
  

  <section class="feature">
    <h2>üß† DSA Assistant</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Paste a DSA question or code snippet</h3>
        <p>Input any coding challenge or part of your solution you're unsure about.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Get AI-powered analysis</h3>
        <p>Understand what‚Äôs working, what‚Äôs not, and why ‚Äî with clean fixes and dry runs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3. Learn the logic</h3>
        <p>Review step-by-step reasoning, edge case handling, and complexity explanation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature">
    <h2>üêû Code Debugger</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Share broken code or error logs</h3>
        <p>Paste your buggy code or describe the issue you're facing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Let MindMate scan and detect issues</h3>
        <p>Our AI inspects code patterns, tracks bugs, and spots logical errors instantly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3. Apply instant suggestions</h3>
        <p>Use the fixed version with insights on what changed and why it works.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature">
    <h2>üöÄ Startup Builder</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Describe your product idea</h3>
        <p>Input your concept, goals, or even the target audience and timeline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Get stack and tool suggestions</h3>
        <p>Receive a curated stack (frontend, backend, infra, APIs) aligned with your needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3. Start building your MVP</h3>
        <p>Follow the AI-generated project plan and development blueprint to execute quickly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature">
    <h2>ü§î Decision Helper</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Ask your question or dilemma</h3>
        <p>Examples: "React vs Vue?", "Should I self-host or use SaaS?"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Get structured insights</h3>
        <p>MindMate weighs pros and cons, asks clarifying questions, and offers multi-angle reasoning.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3. Choose with confidence</h3>
        <p>Make a decision backed by logic, not guesswork.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Start Your Journey with MindMate</h2>
    <a href="<%= user ? '/member/dashboard' : '/login' %>" class="btn-primary">Start Using MindMate</a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
